article_id:1790,category_name:Updates,title_name:Regarding Adjustments to the Alberian Battle Royale with Version 2.2.0,image_path:,message:<div>This notification contains information regarding adjustments to the Alberian Battle Royale with the release of Version 2.2.0.</div><div><br></div><div>■Schedule and Availability Update</div><div>With the release of Version 2.2.0, the schedule for the Alberian Battle Royale will be updated as follows:</div><div><br></div><div>Before: <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606284000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606456799"></span></div><div>After: <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606543200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606715999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606888800"></span>, the Alberian Battle Royale will be available every week from <span class="local_weekly_time" data-local_date="1670997600"></span> to <span class="local_weekly_time" data-local_date="1671170340"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■KO Counter Update and Reset</div><div>In Version 2.2.0 and beyond, defeating AI-controlled enemies, such as goblins and manticores, while playing the Alberian Battle Royale will no longer increase your KO count. Alongside this change, the &quot;Total KOs&quot; and &quot;Highest KO Streak&quot; counters will be reset around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606201200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Adjustments to Earned Battle Points</div><div>The amount of battle points earned based on your rank among other players when the battle ends will be adjusted. In addition, players will earn additional battle points based on the number of KOs that they inflicted during the battle.</div><div><br></div><div>■Addition of Monthly Battle Point Rewards</div><div>Rewards based on the total amount of battle points earned in a month will be added and will be available to collect each month.</div><div>Note: Monthly battle point rewards added at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606543200"></span> will be available until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394399"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Addition to the Treasure Trade Lineup</div><div>A section will be added to the Alberian Battle Royale Treasure Trade that resets every month. The currently available lineup will remain available under the &quot;Special&quot; tab.</div><div>Note: The items in the monthly lineup added at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606543200"></span> will be available until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1609394399"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Endeavors</div><div>Normal endeavors that task players with participating in the Alberian Battle Royale will be added at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1606543200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1605592800,update_time1605591714